section#values

  a(id="values" href="#values")
    h2 dynamic values

  p The `=` symbol indicates that the value should be an expression. An
    | expression can include values from the data passed to the template or
    | any valid javascript.

  pre.input
    code.
      h1 = 'Hello, ' + name

  p Mineral detects `console.log`-like statements.
  pre.input
    code.
      h1 = 'Hello %s', foo
